com.pipe42.data

Class DatabaseSQLite

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pipe42.data.DatabaseSQLite
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DatabaseIO

    public class DatabaseSQLite
extends java.lang.Object
implements DatabaseIO
    These are all the methods relating to implementing SQliteUtilities as a database. This class should not be called directly. Instead use the for that. In this case the Main method initiates a "factory" object through which we can call any method independent of the underlying database.
    Since:
    0.2.0
    See Also:
    DatabaseFactoryProvider, DatabaseIO, Main
